# LinkedIn/Indeed search queries — EXAMPLE
# Copy this file to config/jsearch_queries.txt and replace with your own searches.
#
# Rules:
#   - 3-4 word natural phrases only. 5+ word keyword strings return 0 LinkedIn results.
#   - One query per line. Blank lines and # comments are ignored.
#   - Validate each query manually in LinkedIn before adding.
#   - 10 queries is a good ceiling; more is not better.
#
# The pipeline is field-agnostic. Replace the queries below with terms for YOUR field.
#
# Examples across fields:
#
# Software engineer:
#   senior backend engineer
#   platform engineer
#   infrastructure engineer
#   staff software engineer
#
# Clinical social worker:
#   clinical social worker
#   LCSW outpatient
#   mental health case manager
#   adult services social worker
#
# Middle school teacher:
#   middle school math teacher
#   7th grade teacher
#   STEM teacher
#
# Nonprofit development director:
#   development director nonprofit
#   major gifts officer
#   fundraising manager
#
# Graphic designer:
#   senior graphic designer
#   brand designer
#   product designer

[replace these lines with your own queries]
